Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.60,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}依次来说说吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.61,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}喂喂，先等等
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.98,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}太刺激的内容
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.40,0:10:39.11,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}放到最后再说吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.32,0:10:43.41,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}现实中满是不如意
