Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.04,EDJP-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}ぶちまけてさ　みんなで笑おう
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.25,EDJP-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}シュワリッ　サイダー弾ける
Dialogue: 3,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.51,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}来来，别客气
Dialogue: 3,0:10:23.72,0:10:28.06,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}迷茫少女们的谈心游戏
Dialogue: 3,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.60,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}依次来说说吧
Dialogue: 3,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.61,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}喂喂，先等等
Dialogue: 3,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.98,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}太刺激的内容
Dialogue: 3,0:10:35.40,0:10:39.11,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}放到最后再说吧
Dialogue: 3,0:10:39.32,0:10:43.41,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}现实中满是不如意
Dialogue: 3,0:10:43.74,0:10:48.04,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那就都塞到瓶子里
Dialogue: 3,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.17,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}准备好参加派对了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.17,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不等你了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.71,0:10:57.21,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}另一个故事就要开始了
Dialogue: 3,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.09,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数气泡呼呼冒出
Dialogue: 3,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.34,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数气泡啵啵破裂
Dialogue: 3,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.93,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}生活就像汽水
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.10,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无论是爸爸妈妈的事
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.40,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}还是闷在心底的回忆
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.48,0:11:15.82,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都会化作气泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.40,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣忧愁又烦恼
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.61,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数往事多纷扰
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.33,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都没关系的
Dialogue: 3,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.49,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事尽怀抱
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.75,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}塞进瓶子使劲摇
Dialogue: 3,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.04,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}噗嗤全部释放　大家一起欢笑
Dialogue: 3,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.25,EDCN-EP08,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}咕噜噜　瞬间满是气泡
